hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm sorry, I'm not interested climax control durex In the UK particularly, as a class-led society, we allow our ancestors’ actions to determine our impression of people far too often. For the last few centuries my forebears were quietly tending fields in Italy. If, instead, they had been fighting for whoever won in one battle or another things would be very different. Big houses, social rank, a better education and the assumption that I’m the right sort of person in certain very lucrative situations would have been the result. As it is, I’m just slightly keener on salami than most people.
